reviewText: met all expectation....something i will enjoy and share....very happy...let me know about any other good fashion dvd...very very happy with the product...

I am a up and coming fashion designer, and I loved the DVD. I bought it because I love and respect all four of the designers featured in the dvd. I found it to be very insightful and uplifting in regards to their lives, passion, journey, and career. Thank you once again A&E.....
